{"tid":1845893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友年初一飛左去寧波","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T15:05:29.000Z","uid":121044,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5474bc0a1a8d7809554bad30e38fc4f518f454f4","tid":1845893,"uid":121044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"佢飛果時仲影相同我講：睇下～今日包機<br />\n宜加叫佢一係唔好番香港/即刻搭飛機番黎，就屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現在佢話照原定計劃年初6先番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住 我識哩啲咁智障 咁自私 真係好慚愧<br />\n但今次唔篤灰都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前運動最嚴重果時....大約11.12月....話食飯....仲問我食唔食吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢把口話自己黃.....大佬我真係救撚命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇咩方法令佢唔好番香港....咁樣真係累死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b299e7dcc711ac0bfb804acd5dd734e595819cc","tid":1845893,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"去國安網舉報佢顛覆國家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過後果唔知會點"},{"pid":"304415ba7c8eb40cc98d31b768ca655d8edc73c6","tid":1845893,"uid":121044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b299e7dcc711ac0bfb804acd5dd734e595819cc","tid":1845893,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"去國安網舉報佢顛覆國家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過後果唔知會點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"有冇第個辦法？唔想搞到佢家破人亡，只係想佢有啲警覺性，唔好再做豬"},{"pid":"9d7040d3fab51e78f750f990edeab73967417f2b","tid":1845893,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"304415ba7c8eb40cc98d31b768ca655d8edc73c6","tid":1845893,"uid":121044,"li